    FIXME: remove this piece of code when Blazor implements `onmouseenter` and `onmouseleave`
    I'm setting the events on JS because `onmouseover` and `onmouseout` causes the tooltip to blink
    when you move the mouse *@
<span @ref="_ref">
    @ChildContent
</span>
